org.openbel.framework.common.record
Class StringColumn

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.record.Column<String>
      org.openbel.framework.common.record.StringColumn

public class StringColumn
extends Column<String>

Represents a Column of type String where the length of the string is arbitrary.

This column implementation pads strings with spaces during encoding if the strings are less than the column's size. During encoding, the padding is removed. Encoding strings with length greater than the column's size will result in truncation.

Author:
Nick Bargnesi
